Q_DESC: Given a set or an array of integers, find if there is subset with a given sum K. It is know as subset sum problem. For example, if array  A = [2,3,5,6,7,8,9] and K = 15, subsets which have K as sum are [ 3,5,7], [7,8], [6,9],[2,5,8]. Answer to the problem will be True.                   Input Format:                                   First line- is the no:of elements in the set.                                                 Then enter the elements in the set                                                     Last line is the sum
